   Requires a minimum of 10 chi to activate. All current chi is consumed,
   and the damage of the strike scales directly with the amount of chi spent.

   This is the Martial Artist's burst-damage counterpart to Flurry. Where
   Flurry converts chi into many weak basic hits, Chi Surge converts chi
   into one massive blow -- Monk internal energy directed through Brawler
   impact methodology.

   Chi cost: ALL current chi (minimum 10)
   Cooldown: 15 rounds
   Damage element: Physical
   Damage formula: base pug damage * (chi spent / 5)
